HIGH SCHOOL ROUNDUP: Abbott Tech volleyball team clinches division title 1 / 5 Back to Gallery 
The Abbott Tech volleyball team clinched Constitution State Conference Western Division title Friday with a 3-0 victory over Kaynor Tech. Marissa Shamansky and Jordan Alexander tallied four kills apiece for the Wolverines, while Rhayssa Louzada had 13 assists. Louzada, Isabella Rodovalho and Alexander added six service points apiece. 
GIRLS VOLLEYBALL 
ABBOTT TECH 3, KAYNOR TECH 0
